      "date": "2011-07-08 19:38:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/9cc37ad2-a999-11e0-b33f-52540025f9af).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
